gov.nih.nci.cabig.caaers.domain.report
Class Report

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.AbstractMutableDomainObject
      gov.nih.nci.cabig.caaers.domain.report.Report
All Implemented Interfaces:
WorkflowAware, gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.DomainObject, gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.GridIdentifiable, gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.MutableDomainObject, java.io.Serializable
public class Report
extends gov.nih.nci.cabig.ctms.domain.AbstractMutableDomainObject
implements WorkflowAware, java.io.Serializable

A report sending schedule for an adverse event. The RuleExecutionService, evaluates pre-defined set of rules over the attributes of an AdverseEvent, and creates a Report.

Author:
Biju Joseph
